{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body><p>更新時間：09:15 2026-04-29 HKT<br/>發佈時間：09:15 2026-04-29 HKT</p>\n<p>發佈時間：09:15 2026-04-29 HKT</p><p>金山郊野公園近筆架山往沙田方向，今（29日）早上約8時，48歲姓江男子到上址行山，其間經過引水道，不慎跣倒跌落引水道內，其他行山人士途經見狀報警求助。消防接報到場，沿路尋找，發現江男已自行爬回路面，並沿山路走出，江兩手肘擦傷，清醒由救護車送院敷治。</p><img alt=\"消防接報到場。梁國峰攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/10a5b18a2144531e76595084df96cc4c/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260429_085743668_1_.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/9a1b3c56be397a26f13cae385d2faddf/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260429_085743668_01_1_.jpg\"/><img alt=\"事主清醒送院。梁國峰攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/a6d4e3b5aca4ddbe2a28cd64862165fa/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260429_085743668_03_1_.jpg\"/><img alt=\"事主手肘擦傷。梁國峰攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/e6a0a3fe9d36cbe0753ea5aa22a09f8f/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260429_085743668_05_1_.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/cbce88367e43fdb961bbb9a8ae55a1aa/2026-04/KakaoTalk_20260429_085743668_06_1_.jpg\"/><p>最Hit</p>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T03:16:17.524612+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":207,"images":5,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}